"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/420249","Ministry of Justice","false","2015-10-14","<p>The estate principles used to determine which buildings were included in the consultation document can be found at: https://consult.justice.gov.uk/digital-communications/proposal-on-the-provision-of-court-and-tribunal-es.</p>","North West Cambridgeshire","Mr Shailesh Vara",,"2015-10-14T15:17:00.02Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/420249/answer","Biography information for Mr Shailesh Vara","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/420249/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/420249/answer",,,,,"54","Justice","Justice","2015-10-09","Courts: Closures","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Justice, what assessment criteria are used to determine court closures.","false","Biography information for Conor McGinn","St Helens North","Conor McGinn","10856"
