iament.uk/resources/420265/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/420265/answer",,,,,"54","Justice","Justice","2015-10-09","Youth Custody: Restraint Techniques","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Justice, how many times force has been used on children for good order and discipline at (a) HM Young Offender Institution Feltham, (b) HM Young Offender Institution Wetherby, (c) HM Young Offender Institution Werrington, (d) HM Young Offender Institution Cookham Wood and (e) Parc Young People's Unit in each of the last three years.","false","Biography information for Jenny Chapman","Darlington","Jenny Chapman","11257"
